import React from 'react'; import Header from './Header'; import Footer from './Footer'; import './FreeWillPage.css'; const FreeWillPage: React.FC = () => { const handleDownload = () => { // Create a simple text file as a placeholder for the will template const willTemplate = `FREE WILL TEMPLATE - Freewill.Ltd This is a blank will template provided by Freewill.Ltd. Please fill out this document with your personal information and wishes. IMPORTANT: This is a basic template. For complex estates or legal questions, please consult with a qualified attorney. WILL OF [YOUR NAME] I, [YOUR FULL NAME], of [YOUR ADDRESS], being of sound mind and memory, do hereby make, publish and declare this to be my Last Will and Testament. 1. REVOCATION OF PRIOR WILLS I hereby revoke all former wills and codicils made by me. 2. EXECUTOR I hereby nominate and appoint [EXECUTOR NAME] as the Executor of this Will. 3. BEQUESTS I give, devise and bequeath all of my property, both real and personal, to [BENEFICIARY NAME]. 4. GUARDIANSHIP If I have minor children, I nominate [GUARDIAN NAME] as guardian of their persons and property. IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand this [DATE] day of [MONTH], [YEAR]. [YOUR SIGNATURE] WITNESSED BY: Witness 1: [NAME] _________________ [SIGNATURE] [DATE] Witness 2: [NAME] _________________ [SIGNATURE] [DATE] --- This template is provided by Freewill.Ltd For more information, visit our website.`; const blob = new Blob([willTemplate], { type: 'text/plain' }); const url = window.URL.createObjectURL(blob); const link = document.createElement('a'); link.href = url; link.download = 'FreeWill_Template.txt'; document.body.appendChild(link); link.click(); document.body.removeChild(link); window.URL.revokeObjectURL(url); }; return (
